<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.1">
<l>veṇṇey viḻuṅki veṟuṅka lattai</l>
<l>veṟpiṭai yiṭṭata ṉōcai kēṭkum</l>
<l>kaṇṇa pirāṉkaṟṟa kalvi taṉṉaik</l>
<l>kākkakil lōmuṉ makaṉaik kāvāy</l>
<l>puṇṇil puḷippeytā lokkum tīmai</l>
<l>puraipurai yālivai ceyya valla</l>
<l>aṇṇaṟkaṇ ṇāṉōr makaṉaip peṟṟa</l>
<l>yacōtai naṅkāyuṉ makaṉaik kūvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We cannot prevent the malicious habits of Lord Kaṇṇa who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having devoured the butter,</l>
<l>threw the empty pots on the stone [floor] to hear the sound.</l>
<l>Restrain your son!</l>
<l>In house after house, he is able to commit such wickedness,</l>
<l rend="indent">as if pouring tamarind [juice] in a wound.</l>
<l>Yaśodā, [you] have a son who has an excellent eye.</l>
<l>My Lady, call your son!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
